General.Name: Techno Medical Public Company Limited
General.Description: Techno Medical Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, trades in medical supplies, tools, and equipment in Thailand. The company operates in two segments, Disposable Equipment and Supplies, and Medical Equipment and Instrument. It also operates nursing-care school, as well as hospital; and provides nursing-care services. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
